title: LG ELECTRONICS 4930W1A069A LG ELECTRONICS 4930W1A069A Microwave Metal Shelf Support
description: This manufacturer-approved metal shelf support (part number 4930W1A069A) is for microwaves.Metal shelf support 4930W1A069A attaches on the side of the microwave and holds the cooking shelf in place.Because high-voltage capacitors in a microwave can retain a lethal electrical charge even when the microwave is unplugged, a service technician should install this part.
